# AIDLC Changes Directory .gitignore
# Place this file at: aidlc-docs/changes/.gitignore
#
# Prevents committing artifacts that should NOT be in Git.
# See rules/08-spec-compliance.md "What should NOT be committed" for rationale.

# Raw AI output (long, not reproducible)
**/ai-drafts/
**/ai-output/
**/raw-ai/

# Debug and temporary files
**/debug.md
**/debug-*.md
**/notes-draft.md
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak

# Multiple draft versions (Git history handles this)
**/drafts/

# Intermediate screenshots and binary artifacts
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.gif
**/*.mp4

# Detailed test reports in HTML format (use CI artifacts)
**/test-report*.html
**/coverage-report/

# Editor and OS artifacts
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Prompt iteration logs (keep only prompts.md at root)
**/prompt-log.md
**/prompt-history.md
